---
title: Taco Soup
---

Brown @hamburger{1-1 1/2%lbs} with @onion{1}(chopped).

Dump the meat and all of the cans: @kidney beans{1%can}, @corn{1%can}, @diced tomatoes{1%can}, and @tomato sauce{1%can} into a #crock pot.

Do not drain!

Leave on low.

Serve with a dollop of @sour cream{} and @cheddar cheese{(shredded)} on top.

Eat with @Fritos corn chips{}.